      "full_name": "Tsybulka Bel",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "Tsybulka-Bel LLC is a Belarussian Agro-company based in the Lida district which is owned by the German national Jörg Dornau. The management of Tsybulka-Bel coordinated with Belarussian state authorities to deploy inmates – including in particular Belarussian political prisoners – as forced laborers at Tsybulka-Bel for fieldwork under inhumane conditions, including the withholding of food and water during extensive work shifts, wholly insufficient protection against extreme weather conditions and arbitrary punishment against prisoners requesting exemptions due to illnesses. Tsybulka-Bel LLC is thus an entity responsible for serious violations of human rights and repression of the democratic opposition Belarus.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}